{"tid":557023,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家抵制年宵","createTime":"2018-02-11T03:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T08:10:10.000Z","uid":63450,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71c0683c9c9c837bfbc0208b3d9013bbf73b803e","tid":557023,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"年宵市場根本已經變左質好多好多年<br />\n<br />\n由以前一家大細開開心心去買下吉買下花 食下平民小食<br />\n<br />\n我今時今日個個攤檔都淨係識買冒牌公仔<br />\n有啲公仔質素甚至差過花園街嗰啲<br />\n冒牌嘅仲要買到好似真貨咁貴<br />\n成百幾二百蚊一隻冒牌公仔<br />\n啲人叫佢減下價佢哋竟然話再減無肉食<br />\n<br />\n間間大專大學嘅學生組織都以自創原創為名<br />\n實情就係想賺番一筆<br />\n個個後生仔都講淘寶買假野<br />\n點知自己都係中國人一鳩樣<br />\n<br />\n啲小食更加唔使講啦＄30一串同冰糖胡佬<br />\n10幾廿蚊幾蚊魚蛋燒賣都有人去買<br />\n仲要好鳩難食<br />\n<br />\n仲有一大班公民黨嘅人喺度做show<br />\n新年流流靜下得唔得<br />\n平時又唔見你哋咁勤力落區<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好再做老襯"},{"pid":"10d8363f2d9fa1342ae066f2698ad4b64f6ec0bf","tid":557023,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"自從三年前喺年宵俾啲大陸人非禮完之後<br />\n我都無再去過"},{"pid":"aaedbe36efb67b3996bf96594574b2e9417613af","tid":557023,"uid":63450,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10d8363f2d9fa1342ae066f2698ad4b64f6ec0bf","tid":557023,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"自從三年前喺年宵俾啲大陸人非禮完之後<br />\n我都無再去過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"Pmed"},{"pid":"d27567f1eaf9989d0009abc7c9591186ef0045da","tid":557023,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:44:53.000Z","msg":"通常只行不買"},{"pid":"63703f1c0ba0a69708546eaf4564a5f687f3dda6","tid":557023,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d27567f1eaf9989d0009abc7c9591186ef0045da","tid":557023,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:44:53.000Z","msg":"通常只行不買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"咁逼 不了 <br />\n如果係想睇公仔上淘寶一樣啦"},{"pid":"b025303333064e67e5d058e95c21c5d971f7cb0a","tid":557023,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"傻鳩先去 十分有趣"},{"pid":"5cd5aecf5c7a022dc3dcc1fe09b2125b2f0456e8","tid":557023,"uid":161649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"而家年宵檔賣嘅野真係好低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口號又抄人 一啲原創野都冇<br />\n頭先行完<br />\n已經聽到有幾檔係到大叫<br />\n[唔駛上淘寶，唔駛去深水埗]<br />\n心諗屌你已經賣緊淘寶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口號都抄街邊平民家品店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cccb8687d8d23c8db5039a77a6e77413bcaa281","tid":557023,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T08:07:55.000Z","msg":"因為現今社會錢先係最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b05a934b0847d543053e30736e9ba740a0adae","tid":557023,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"岩呀"}]}